after each sentence

*Potrebna mi je pomoć.* (I need help.)
*Potrebna je nova strategija.* (A new strategy is needed.)
*Njegova pomoć nam je potrebna.* (His help is needed by us.)
*Potrebno je vreme da se sve završi.* (Time is needed to finish everything.)
*Potrebna je disciplina da bi se uspelo.* (Discipline is needed to succeed.)